      "text": "News » Sports » Cricket BRILLIANT! Lokesh Rahul SHUTS down fan who tried to troll him for his poor form \nLokesh Rahul certainly seems to have taken a leaf out of R Ashwin's book in terms of dealing with trolls on social media. Last Updated: Tuesday, February 28, 2017 - 14:38 0 Follow @ZeeNewsSports \nNew Delhi: Indian opener Lokesh Rahul, who looked convincing across formats in 2016, has been struggling to rediscover his mojo in 2017. \nThe Bangalore batsman had a forgettable limited-overs series against England, where he managed to score just 125 runs from six matches. Even in the one-off Test against Bangladesh, Rahul failed to find his rhythm and was dismissed for scores of 2 and 10 rspectively. \nWhen Rahul posted an update on Twitter on Tuesday, one of the fans tried to troll him for his poor form. \nHere's what the fan tweeted: @klrahul11 @ashwinravi99 ye sab chhodo .. runs kaise bane uspe dhyan de .. \n— BeingChirag Dave (@BeingChiragDave) February 28, 2017 \nRahul, who usually doesn't reply to trolls, was tempted to leave a reply and here's what he tweeted back: Plz come and teach us bhai. Im sure aapko pata hain kaise banate hain runs. https://t.co/KyiuAWFusz \n— K L Rahul (@klrahul11) February 28, 2017 \nRahul was followed by premier Indian off-spinner Ravichandran Ashwin on Twitter today. \nThe stylish right-hander certainly seems to have taken a leaf out of the offie's book in terms of dealing with trolls on social media. First Published: Tuesday, February 28, 2017 - 14:38 More from zeenews ",
