      "text": "\n The Parish Priest of St.Patrick's Catholic Church in Bangalore in India during a Sunday Mass, made an Ironical statement. He said to CHRISTIAN that the best way to behave as a CHRISTIAN during this 40days lenten period is to take LOTS of BEER.\n\n\nLol, You don't have to be Scared or Perplexed; He didn't actually mean what you are thinking in your heart right now.  Below is actually what he meant:\n\n B-BIBLE: Read your Bible.This is God's given time, you are expected to be spiritually enriched with the word of God.\n\n E-EMPATHY: Feel empathy for the poor, less Privileged, Motherless, the Fatherless, the Maniac, the disable and neglected. Take good care of them and Show Constant Love to them.\n\nE-EUCHARIST: Go for mass frequently besides Sunday's.If possible everyday. Take in the Body of Christ Daily.\n\nR-RECONCILIATION: This is the best time to reconcile with those we have hurt, disappointed in the past, those we are in Malice with. Seek forgiveness and make Peace. Restore our relationship with God and one another.\n\n\nHave a wonderful and joyful Lent and do not forget your BEER.\n\nHappy New Month From MY NEWS VILLA EDITORS!! ",
