      "title": "ORU MEXICAN APARATHA BANGALORE THEATRES LIST SHOW TIMINGS, TOVINO THOMAS, TOM EMMATTY",
      "text": "\n\nBANGALORE 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' RELEASE SCREENING THEATRES LIST, SHOW TIMINGS INFO STARRING TOVINO THOMAS, DIRECTED BY TOM EMMATTY DETAILS PROVIDED HERE. MOLLYWOOD ORU MEXICAN APARATHA IS SLATED FOR 03-03-2017 RELEASE IN KARNATAKA CITY BANGALORE AND HERE ARE THE MOVIE THEATRES LIST WITH SHOW TIMINGS. MARCH 3RD, 2017 BANGALORE CINEMAS RELEASE 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' SHOWING THEATRES LIST AND SHOW TIMINGS LISTED HERE. BANGALORE FILM THEATRES SHOWING TOVINO THOMAS ACTING IN ORU MEXICAN APARATHA also stars Roopesh Peethambaran, Neeraj Madhav, Sunil Sukhada, Gayathri Suresh, Sudhy Koppa, Kalabhavan Shajon in important roles. This film is of genre ROMCOM, political drama. the protagonist of this film Tovino Thomas has acted in movies namely Grisaille, Jaalakam, Prabhuvinte Makkal, ABCD, August Club, 7th Day, Koothara, You Too Brutus, Onnam Loka Mahayudham, Ennu Ninte Moideen (Won, SIIMA, Asiavision Awards -Best Supporting Actor), Charlie, Style, Monsoon Mangoes, 2 Penkuttikal, Guppy, Ezra. Roopesh Peethambaran who was well known to audience as Junior Aadu Thoma (Thomas Chacko) in Sphadikam had also acted in a tv series named Pranavam (child artist). Neeraj Madhav has acted in movies namely Buddy, Memories, Drishyam, Oru Indian Pranayakadha, 1983, Apothecary, Sapthamashree Thaskaraha, Homely Meals, Mariyam Mukku, Oru Vadakkan Selfie, Madhura Naranga, KL.10 Pathu, Jamna Pyari, Kunjiramayanam, Charlie, Adi Kapyare Kootamani, Oozham. Sunil Sukhada has acted in movies namely Campus Diary, Romanov, Marubhoomiyile Aana, Inspector Dawood Ibrahim, Kismath, Pa Va, Pretham, Zoom, White, James and Alice. \n\n\nTOVINO THOMAS 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' BANGALORE RELEASE THEATRES LIST, SHOW TIMINGS   \nBANGALORE ORU MEXICAN APARATHA MALAYALAM MOVIE SHOW TIMINGS, THEATRES LIST DETAILS. RELEASE DATE IS 03-03-2017 I.E. 3RD MARCH. CAST, CREW, TRAILER DETAILS POSTED HERE. \nGayathri Suresh (winner of Femina Miss Kerala 2014 beauty pageant) has earlier acted in films namely Jamna Pyari, Karinkunnam 6'S, Ore Mugham. \nBANGALORE RELEASE 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' CINEMAS LIST, SHOW TIMINGS   \nDIRECTOR, SCREENPLAY > TOM EMMATTY \nPRODUCER > ANOOP KANNAN \nWRITER > JUDE ANTHANY JOSEPH \nLEAD ACTORS, SUPPORTING ROLES > TOVINO THOMAS, ROOPESH PEETHAMBARAN, NEERAJ MADHAV, SUNIL SUKHADA, GAYATHRI SURESH, SUDHY KOPPA, KALABHAVAN SHAJON, JINO JOHN, ANJALI P NAIR, MEGHA MATHEW. \nMUSIC DIRECTOR > MANIKANDAN AYYAPPAN \nCINEMATOGRAPHER > PRAKASH VELAYUDHAN \nEDITOR > SHAMEER MUHAMMED \nPRODUCTION COMPANY > ANOOP KANNAN STORIES \n\n\n'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' MOLLYWOOD MOVIE THEATRES LIST, SHOW TIMING IN  BANGALORE  \nBANGALORE 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' KARNATAKA STATE MOLLYWOOD MOVIE RELEASE DATE IS 03-03-2017, 3RD MARCH  \nKalabhavan Shajohn recently acted films are namely Urumbukal Urangarilla, Amar Akbar Anthony, Vishwasam Athalle Ellam, Rajamma @ Yahoo, Pavada, Oppam \n\nBANGALORE MOVIE SHOW TIMINGS, THEATRES LIST OF 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' STARRING TOVINO THOMAS,  ROOPESH PEETHAMBARAN, GAYATHRI SURESH \nBANGALORE ORU MEXICAN APARATHA MALAYALAM FILM 3RD MARCH 2017 RELEASE IN KARNATAKA STATE THE THEATRES LIST SHOWING MOLLYWOOD MOVIE ORU MEXICAN APARATHA MAY BE ACCURATE ONLY FOR FIRST 5 DAYS OF FILM (ORU MEXICAN APARATHA) RELEASE. PLEASE CHECK WITH THEATRES PERSONALLY BEFORE WATCHING THE CINEMA (ORU MEXICAN APARATHA) AS NEW MOVIES WILL BE SCHEDULED FOR RELEASES EVERY WEEKEND. \n\nCINEMA HALLS NAMES LIST IN BANGALORE SCREENING 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' DIRECTED BY TOM EMMATTY \nBANGALORE ORU MEXICAN APARATHA MOVIE SHOWING CINEMAS LIST, SHOW TIME PUBLISHED BELOW \n\n<<<<<<<<< >>>>>>>>> \nCINEPOLIS> ETA MALL, MAGADI ROAD \n10>00 PM \n\n\n\n\nINNOVATIVE MULTIPLEX> MARATHAHALLI \n10>00 PM \n\n\n\n\nGOPALAN MINIPLEX> SIGNATURE MALL, OLD MADRAS ROAD \n09>30 PM \n\n\n\n\nHMT DIGITAL 4K CINEMA> JALAHALLI \n07>00 PM \n\n\n\n\nLAKSHMI DIGITAL 2K CINEMA> TAVAREKERE \n09>45 PM \n\n\n\n\n<<<<<<<<< >>>>>>>>> \n\n\n<<<<<<<<< >>>>>>>>> MORE THEATRES WILL BE UPDATED SHORTLY <<<<<<<<< >>>>>>>>> \n\n\n<<<<<<<<< >>>>>>>>> SHOW TIMINGS MAY VARY AND ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE <<<<<<<<< >>>>>>>>> \n\n\n\nBANGALORE  RELEASE 'ORU MEXICAN APARATHA' TRAILER MOLLYWOOD MOVIE   \nBANGALORE KARNATAKA STATE RELEASE ORU MEXICAN APARATHA -> ROMCOM GENRE MOVIE WATCH TRAILER STARRING TOVINO THOMAS IS DIRECTED BY TOM EMMATTY & PRODUCED BY ANOOP KANNAN \n\n",
